cell.name: A1
cell.simple-value: 馆藏档案声像档案单项统计表

dataset.name: 案卷统计zpda-bgqx
dataset.sql: SELECT bgqx, COUNT(DISTINCT ajh) as count FROM zpda WHERE (bgqx = '长期' or bgqx = '永久') and sxh = '001' GROUP BY bgqx;

dataset.name: 卷内文件统计zpda-bgqx
dataset.sql: SELECT bgqx,COUNT(*) as count from zpda WHERE ys not like '%[^0-9]%' and (bgqx = '长期' or bgqx = '永久') GROUP BY bgqx ORDER BY bgqx;

dataset.name: 卷内文件统计zpda统计
归档文件统计ypda-bgqx
dataset.sql: SELECT bgqx,COUNT(*) as count from ypda WHERE ys not like '%[^0-9]%' and (bgqx = '长期' or bgqx = '永久' or bgqx = '定期' or bgqx = '30年') GROUP BY bgqx ORDER BY bgqx;
